Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:09.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道自己是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.78,0:00:12.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,並不是喪失了記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.86,0:00:16.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,附近有醫院 現在就和你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.66,0:00:18.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.99,0:00:21.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只不過在躲避的時候摔的動作大了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.79,0:00:26.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道自己是長門有希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.79,0:00:28.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.42,0:00:34.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我無法意識到這是我自己的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.52,0:02:13.44,Title - blur - 20,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(808,880)\bord0\blur10\fad(695,695)}小長門有希的消失I
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.52,0:02:13.44,Title - 20,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(808,880)\fad(695,695)}小長門有希的消失I
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雨下個不停呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天吃咖哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.04,0:02:28.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她是朝倉涼子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.71,0:02:35.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我 長門有希的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,醃菜還有剩下的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 醃菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.52,0:02:49.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼 差點被車撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.27,0:02:52.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是經常在身邊幫助我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.90,0:02:54.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受傷了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.69,0:02:56.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼叫沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先把衣服脫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.45,0:03:01.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,態度稍微有些強硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.24,0:03:03.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小題大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.66,0:03:07.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小題大作？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這怎麼會是小題大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論是差點被車撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是只受了擦傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她真心在擔心著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真心的擔心著長門有希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.97,0:04:10.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.53,0:04:24.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在讀什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 不會念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.61,0:05:01.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和這個人接觸稍微會有些困惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.90,0:05:07.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我知道長門有希對他抱有的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨天真是危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從朝倉那裡聽來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她對他的抱有的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的我無法感受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.43,0:05:28.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受的傷沒大礙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.47,0:05:38.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我知道這個人很重視我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在擔心我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在說什麼呢 那是當然的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.53,0:05:53.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個人很溫柔 並沒有深層次的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.75,0:05:55.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.71,0:06:08.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是因為他是這種人長門才會喜歡上的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一如既往的情景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,味道怎麼樣 要再多加點起司嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.36,0:06:25.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.28,0:06:27.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一如既往的餐桌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.62,0:06:32.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你 關心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.92,0:06:45.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而我不是一如既往的長門有希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.97,0:06:56.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然 還有另一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.61,0:07:10.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個人很敏銳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我總覺得你是別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.37,0:07:21.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你能說明一下到底是怎麼回事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.25,0:07:28.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不清楚自己到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和喪失記憶有些區別呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感覺像是在讀著別人的日記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.89,0:07:41.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然有記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但無法認為這是我自己的體驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.94,0:07:47.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是不管怎麼說 記憶還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以這樣扮演長門有希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話雖然是那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼沒有第一時間告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在也為時不晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起去醫院看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的我對於你來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或許是異常的長門有希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個判斷並沒有錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.09,0:08:18.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我無法認可自己是異常的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是我認可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就會變得孤單一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以就隱瞞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.65,0:08:34.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 我沒有考慮到你的處境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過早點問了你太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,後來再改變態度就太麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像以往一樣接觸就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對吧 長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那樣就可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.42,0:08:54.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的確 我想要你恢復到原來的長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.51,0:08:59.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即便如此 我也不應該否定你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.18,0:09:04.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本來最困惑的是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是現在的長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我得幫助你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.19,0:09:10.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.74,0:09:17.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明天還是向學校請假去醫院看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算現在沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了身體著想 還是先去一趟比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然我剛說過不應該否定你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了 我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,頭部雖然有輕微擦傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.93,0:09:45.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但腦部沒有異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.89,0:09:47.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會危及生命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門你說的癥狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.94,0:09:55.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概是因為強烈刺激引起的暫時的記憶障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過看不到病情我不敢下結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先入院一個星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.08,0:10:01.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能不入院嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在也能正常生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.46,0:10:12.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以防萬一我也會隨時都能和她在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.21,0:10:17.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想特殊對待現在的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼就在自家觀察吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.64,0:10:26.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也沒辦法保障人院之後一定會好轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在旁邊陪著的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她也會感到安心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.52,0:10:36.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大腦在睡眠的時候會整理自己的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以要好好睡覺 好好吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要焦急 安心生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,緊張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為你在旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.51,0:11:02.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人格變了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道你無法輕易接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.52,0:11:07.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 能借我玩玩遊戲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒有帶過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的啊 人格變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,輕易的就接受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.41,0:11:26.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實昨天就感到有些違和感了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.37,0:11:31.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許會拜託你照顧一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那倒沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種狀態下讓她來學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是說現在的長門覺得沒問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來學校的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.43,0:11:48.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是說要繼續假裝成原來的長門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直扮演別人怎麼說也太難受了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.81,0:11:54.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.52,0:11:59.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我確實不是以前的長門有希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過現在的我也是長門有希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.36,0:12:04.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣子就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼接下來就涼宮他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天不來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.87,0:12:17.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 春日他們的話 說是暫時來不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為有期末測試前的補習課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔？升學學校真累人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還說結束了就給我做好覺悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.97,0:12:28.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夏天要玩個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們這邊也一樣有測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這段時間能安靜的度過是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 上課怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,學習能跟上嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.82,0:12:44.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題 只是感覺記憶不是自己的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知識一類的都在腦子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能再給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.45,0:12:56.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會做有損長門有希名譽的事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我並不是這個意思的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.47,0:13:07.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭啦 我不是那個意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是沒有辦法的事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要在意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.82,0:13:28.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝 長門的事也謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你能接受現在的長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.99,0:13:36.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她說害怕要是說出自己不正常的話會變成一個人而寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,覺得我們會離她而去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.34,0:13:47.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖不怎麼明白 但那一定會不安的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉你也別洩氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.18,0:13:55.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過也不能隨便處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是太過擔心長門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.73,0:14:02.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不是因為這份感情而使長門更加的緊張？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不想被阿虛這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不想被你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明跟我一樣擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.49,0:14:12.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,通常說教時會對自己的錯置之不理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你覺得應該怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.12,0:14:17.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我希望長門變回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但現在的長門也放心不下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘛 當她同伴就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.88,0:14:26.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.59,0:14:28.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是當然的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.85,0:14:36.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你喝甜的還是喝茶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.24,0:14:51.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個 你想要哪個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.95,0:14:53.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.37,0:14:54.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我要茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你喜歡看書？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 非常感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼有機會的話一起去圖書館嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 交給我吧 約好囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我做了個夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.33,0:15:44.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,內容完全不記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安 看你還想睡的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很晚才醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是遊戲變成了書啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熬夜是治不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我去準備早餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.77,0:16:04.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你先去洗把臉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要幾塊麵包？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來洗碗 你去換衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.83,0:16:26.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快去換衣服 我會幫你再烤塊麵包的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.30,0:16:36.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,食慾沒有變化啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早 阿虛今天也是勉強勉強的時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,考試期間可是很痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.99,0:16:56.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真好啊 優等生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.07,0:16:57.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一臉從容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.24,0:17:01.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我是在影子下努力的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.29,0:17:04.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從容的背後 壓力也不斷累積
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到達臨界點的話 會有「好事」發生喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的假的？會變成什麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.59,0:17:15.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那樣吧 像最近的年輕人那樣 從背後突然把阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底還是用我來發洩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說回來 長門沒問題吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.52,0:17:26.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上課？她本人都說沒問題 只好相信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天有體育對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.36,0:17:35.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但不管怎麼說 只能用溫暖的眼光守護了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼這題就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 你來做一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.96,0:17:48.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.42,0:17:50.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然有擔心著能不能跟上課程進度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但沒預想到這展開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,砰的一下然後唬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.47,0:18:01.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 萬一出什麼事我們就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 正解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊咧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們兩個在幹嘛啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門同學 成績不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還以為長門是個文靜的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來那麼厲害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我做的不好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊？什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感覺你很擔心的看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都寫在臉上啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.14,0:18:47.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.52,0:18:51.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 實際上非常擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過跑的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.69,0:18:57.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到最後 並沒有要擔心的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.83,0:19:08.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 好像沒人發覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使如此 我也會注意言行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門同學？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我記憶裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門有希固有的口癖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.65,0:19:37.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,數學的答案做得很正規啊 很好懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,問題解得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但無法詳盡解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.53,0:19:45.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我提前看書複習了一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道是這樣才熬夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,表面上雖然不讓人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但真的努力的演著長門有希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝款待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.72,0:20:11.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以把我的也吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上也是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我說一下就好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會給你做大份點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不必那麼顧忌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.24,0:20:25.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是那樣 只是我那時很害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.58,0:20:31.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說來也是 朝倉比較遲鈍嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欸 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行了 完全不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.81,0:20:52.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讀書？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為很快就要測試了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.90,0:20:55.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊的數字拿來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇塞 好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼這個呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先解這邊的 然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 那 這邊怎麼做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.08,0:21:14.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.54,0:21:25.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以後只要跟長門請教 就不用向朝倉低頭還要看她臉色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.64,0:21:27.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,惡人的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.39,0:21:32.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但能被依靠也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.02,0:21:37.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們還在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.81,0:21:38.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快要考試了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天開始社團活動要停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,班會課上應該有說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.36,0:21:46.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快 回去 回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.66,0:21:55.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,班會課的時候我在看書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.87,0:21:58.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在發呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就說怎麼朝倉沒有來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.96,0:22:02.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說她怎麼沒告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回去的時候她腦子裡只想著要買的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.63,0:22:07.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.72,0:22:10.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過真困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.47,0:22:12.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還有想問的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.97,0:22:15.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能用社辦真傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.44,0:22:19.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.94,0:22:20.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,約定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.52,0:22:23.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起去圖書館的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.82,0:22:25.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在 要去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.65,0:22:27.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 這麼說也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.74,0:22:29.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.12,0:22:30.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 走吧
